An Act relating to teacher preparation; directing the
Commission for Educational Quality and Accountability
to establish and maintain TeachForwardOK for certain
time period; providing purpose; directing the
Commission to issue certain request for proposals
within certain time period; providing process for
program application; directing the Commission to
prescribe application form; directing the Commission
to establish criteria for applicant approval;
directing the Commission to award grants to approved
applicants, subject to availability of funding;
allowing the Commission to use certain funds for
implementation; providing for use of grants;
directing certain provider to evaluate certain
minimum factors; requiring evaluation reports to be
electronically submitted to approved applicants and
the Commission; directing teacher education program
to electronically submit a report response to the
Commission within certain time period; directing
report responses to prioritize certain approaches;
directing the Commission to review report responses
and select certain program to receive certain funding
for certain purpose, subject to availability of
funding; directing the Commission to electronically
submit certain report by certain date; providing for
promulgation of rules; and providing for
